{
  "name": "Invocation: Maddening Hex",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "Icons_JGB/Misc/curse.png",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: hex spell or a warlock feature that curses</em></p>\n<p>As a bonus action, you cause a psychic disturbance around the target cursed by your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/hex\" data-tooltip-href=\"//www.dndbeyond.com/spells/2317-tooltip?disable-webm=1&amp;disable-webm=1\">hex</a>&nbsp;spell or by a warlock feature of yours, such as Hexblade&rsquo;s Curse or Sign of Ill Omen. When you do so, you deal psychic damage to the cursed target and each creature of your choice that you can see within 5 feet of it. The psychic damage equals your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1 damage). To use this invocation, you must be able to see the cursed target, and it must be within 30 feet of you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">FoundryVTT</strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">: This is not automated</span></p>",
